    "open_to_sit_in": true,
    "session_story": "London's longest-running free jazz jam, going strong for 25+ years. Alan Weekes \u2014 session credits include Art Blakey, Courtney Pine and Joss Stone \u2014 holds court every Sunday night from 8pm, often running past 3am. The house band anchors proceedings but the real magic is who drops in unannounced: Mark Kavuma, Ruben Fox and Cleveland Watkiss have all appeared. Clifford Jarvis, original drummer and Blue Note recording artist, was a founding member. Hackney's best-kept secret \u2014 Alan Weekes's own description.",
