    "scraper_notes": "",
    "description": "The Dalston institution. Guitarist Alan Weekes has led this Sunday night session for over 18 years at the pub formerly known as Uncle Sam's \u2014 with regular guests including Mark Kavuma, Mussinghi Brian Edwards and Shane Forbes dropping in. Expect proper post-bop jams that run late into the night."
